                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040215-70-defend591 t18040215-70-punish398"></join>
               Confined one month in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
